# WELCOME
1. Run the app
2. You will find search EditText file to search any movie (minimum 3 characters you should type)
3. After typing the movie name the movie picture appears.
4. Select on the movie to open in detailed view.
5. Click on like symbol(FloatingActionButton) to save the movie details in to DB. (save 5 to 6 movies)
6. Click on bottom navigation bar to see saved movies.
7. Swipe to delete the saved movies and also undo the deleted item by clicking on the UNDO button on the Snackbar(when appeared).